"Welcome to Planet" = "欢迎来到 Planet";
"Build and publish and follow websites on IPFS" = "在 IPFS 上构建、发布和关注网站";
"Manage multiple IPNS ready to be linked to your ENS" = "管理多个可关联到 ENS 的 IPNS";
