"Continue" = "继续";

"Mark All as Read" = "标记为已读";
"Unfollow" = "取消关注";

"Do you want to save your changes as a draft?" = "要将更改保存为草稿吗？";

"Are you sure you want to unfollow this planet?" = "确定要取消关注这个 Planet 吗？";

"Here are your archived Planets. Archived planets are not auto published or updated. You can unarchive them from here." = "这些是已归档的网站。已归档的网站不会自动发布或更新。你可以在这里取消归档。";


"Are you sure you want to delete %@? This action cannot be undone." = "确定要删除 %@ 吗？此操作无法撤销。";

"Are you sure you want to delete this post?\n\n%@?\n\nThis action cannot be undone." = "确定要删除这篇帖子吗？\n\n%@\n\n此操作无法撤销。";

"Would you like to use new library location at" = "是否要使用新的数据文件位置：";

"current database including following planets will be replaced with contents at this location" = "当前数据库（包括关注的网站）将被此位置中的内容替换。";

"When you tip a creator, transactions will be sent to the selected Ethereum network." = "打赏创作者时，交易会发送到所选的 Ethereum 网络。";

"Are you sure you want to archive this planet? Archived planets will not be auto updated. You can later unarchive it from settings." = "确定要归档这个 Planet 吗？归档的 Planet 不会自动更新。之后可以在设置中取消归档。";

"Planet lets you build and host your website on your Mac without requiring a centralized service." = "Planet 可以让你直接在 Mac 上构建和托管网站，不需要中心化服务。";

"You can also use Planet to follow the content creators you like." = "你也可以用 Planet 关注喜欢的内容创作者。";

"The big difference is that there is no middle layer between you and the content creators you follow." = "最大的区别是，你和关注的内容创作者之间没有中间层。";

"You will receive the latest updates in a peer-to-peer manner." = "你会以点对点方式收到最新更新。";

"The slug is the part of the URL that identifies the article. It should be unique and contain only lowercased letters, numbers, and hyphens." = "slug 是 URL 中标识文章的部分。 它应该是唯一的，并且仅包含小写字母、数字和连字符。";

"If you want this article to redirect to an external link, enter the URL here." = "如果希望这篇文章重定向到外部链接，请在这里输入 URL。";

"This domain will be used in places that need a domain prefix, like for RSS or Podcast feeds." = "这个域将用于需要域前缀的地方，比如 RSS 或播客提要。";

"Are you sure you want to archive this planet? Archived planets will not be auto published. You can later unarchive it from settings." = "确定要归档这个 Planet 吗？归档的 Planet 不会自动发布。之后可以在设置中取消归档。";

"Please input an integer for sorting, entries with smaller numbers will be ranked first." = "请输入一个整数进行排序，数字较小的条目将排在前面。";

"Articles of the Page type are not listed on the blog index page, nor are they included in the RSS feed." = "页面类型的文章不会在博客索引页上列出，也不包含在 RSS 源中。";

"Are you sure you want to delete this article? This action will remove it from your feed. However, if the article is still available on the source, it will reappear in your feed the next time you refresh it." = "确定要删除这篇文章吗？此操作会将它从你的订阅中移除。不过，如果原始来源仍可访问，下次刷新时它会再次出现。";


